        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 33. Cnemaspis affinis from Penang Hill, Pulau Pinang, Penang, Peninsular Malaysia. Upper left: adult male (LSUDPC 9078) in the dark color pattern phase. Lower left: adult female (LSUDPC 9079) in the light color pattern phase. Upper right: microhabitat of C. affinis on Penang Hill. Lower right: ventral coloration of male (left) and female (right) C. affinis. Photographs by LLG." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4949632/files/figure.png" .

